\[ RRFScore(d \in D) = \sum_{r \in R} \frac{1}{k+r(d)} \] <p>其中k为一个参数，默认设置为60，r(d)为当前排序的idx(从1开始)，RRF只考虑每次排序的位置，丢弃了排序中数据对应的分数。在实际的使用效果来看，RRF比单独的lexical search和单独的semantic search的效果要好。</p> <pre><code>def reciprocal_rank_fusion(search_results_dict, k=60):
    fused_scores = {}
    print("Initial individual search result ranks:")
    for query, doc_scores in search_results_dict.items():
        print(f"For query '{query}': {doc_scores}")

    for query, doc_scores in search_results_dict.items():
        for rank, (doc, score) in enumerate(sorted(doc_scores.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)):
            if doc not in fused_scores:
                fused_scores[doc] = 0
            previous_score = fused_scores[doc]
            fused_scores[doc] += 1 / (rank + k)
            print(f"Updating score for {doc} from {previous_score} to {fused_scores[doc]} based on rank {rank} in query '{query}'")

    reranked_results = {doc: score for doc, score in sorted(fused_scores.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)}
    print("Final reranked results:", reranked_results)
    return reranked_results
